&lt;p class=&quot;Lexical__paragraph&quot;&gt;Proton continues to grow rapidly as increasing numbers of people across the globe seek greater privacy controls of their information online. To accelerate our growth, we are seeking a senior leader to drive engineering for one of our many existing or upcoming Products.&lt;/p&gt;
