 shape the overall privacy ecosystem.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are looking for an unconventional product marketing leader who marries a sharp, practical&amp;nbsp;understanding of the end user, with a&lt;br&gt;● 12-15 years of experience in a product marketing role in B2C tech companies preferably in&amp;nbsp;online privacy, cybersecurity, productivity and other SaaS contexts.&lt;br&gt;● Voracious early adopter of new technologies across diverse fields from privacy to artificial&amp;nbsp;intelligence, and cryptocurrency to c

