&lt;ul class=&quot;Lexical__ul Lexical__ul--depth-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;Lexical__listItem&quot; value=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Maintain, optimize, and enhance our core security monitoring toolkit (SIEM, sensors, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;Lexical__listItem&quot; value=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Design, build, and continuously refine meaningful alerts, transforming raw infrastructure events into high-fidelity detections.&lt;/li&gt;
